msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 40: Bill was more traditional by today’s standards but quite on the leading edge of psychology for that time. Goodrich spoke with John Gittinger before his death expressly to discuss Bill’s role with A Co...
#: paragraph:40,sentence:186
msgid "In that conversation, he told John that Bill had mentioned his fear of losing the research grants funded indirectly by Gittinger if he had learned of his involvement with A Course In Miracles."
msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 40: Bill was more traditional by today’s standards but quite on the leading edge of psychology for that time. Goodrich spoke with John Gittinger before his death expressly to discuss Bill’s role with A Co...
#: paragraph:40,sentence:187
