#: paragraph:42,sentence:196
msgid "Also, the paymaster in charge of sending grant-related funds to Bill, a personal friend of Whit Whitson, has stated unequivocally that none of Bill’s funding ever came through MKUltra, a controversial experimental project."
msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 42: It is important to correct and clarify some false and misleading information currently on the Internet concerning Bill’s years with the CIA. After Bill’s death, John Gittinger himself stressed that al...
#: paragraph:42,sentence:197
msgid "Some Internet articles falsely state that Bill was funded through that project."
msgstr ""

