#: paragraph:43,sentence:201
msgid "She speculated he may have left the Agency for other institutions in order to search for a hard scientific basis for the derived assessments, as that type of research was not part of his primary job there—testing and evaluating potential intelligence officers."
msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 43: Bill had seemed restless even as he began his work at the CIA, perhaps realizing this was only a point along his career path but not a long-term commitment. In 1953, after gaining experience with the ...
#: paragraph:43,sentence:202
