#: paragraph:47,sentence:226
msgid "I’ll have to have it in fifteen minutes.” I would go to my typewriter and dash off what he wanted"
msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 47: Regarding his time there, Bill wrote of his “lunch time” experiences with the famous and driven Dr. Wolff: At first I thought he really meant for us to have lunch, but that was ridiculous. I could nev...
#: paragraph:47,sentence:227
