msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 50: This assignment, initiated indirectly from the CIA, both frightened and fascinated thirty-two-year-old Bill—a real, live, James Bond-type secret mission where he knew only as much as was provided at a...
#: paragraph:50,sentence:243
msgid "As there were only a handful of passengers, Bill and Harriet met almost immediately and became friends."
