#. Paragraph 50: This assignment, initiated indirectly from the CIA, both frightened and fascinated thirty-two-year-old Bill—a real, live, James Bond-type secret mission where he knew only as much as was provided at a...
#: paragraph:50,sentence:244
msgid "She later told her sister, with whom I spoke in 2007, that after a few days she realized Bill was “put on board to grill her.” She was right."
msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 50: This assignment, initiated indirectly from the CIA, both frightened and fascinated thirty-two-year-old Bill—a real, live, James Bond-type secret mission where he knew only as much as was provided at a...
#: paragraph:50,sentence:245
msgid "He took notes on thin paper and kept them hidden in his pockets."
msgstr ""

#. Paragraph 50: This assignment, initiated indirectly from the CIA, both frightened and fascinated thirty-two-year-old Bill—a real, live, James Bond-type secret mission where he knew only as much as was provided at a...
#: paragraph:50,sentence:246
